{"tid":304449,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)陰陽師 安倍晴明","createTime":"2017-07-01T01:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T04:30:32.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e4088df2eb7679178c260a63e2307a38191859","tid":304449,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Y8VmsIhnDl1mn9ZLGh5eNtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=1a3b306e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Y8VmsIhnDl1mn9ZLGh5eNtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=8c047df7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Y8VmsIhnDl1mn9ZLGh5eNtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=e13f666a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://userdisk.webry.biglobe.ne.jp/005/442/49/N000/000/011/127866583764516231377_onmyouji-nw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fuserdisk.webry.biglobe.ne.jp%2F005%2F442%2F49%2FN000%2F000%2F011%2F127866583764516231377_onmyouji-nw1.jpg&h=5266085f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.公元794年，日本桓武天皇時期，京都長岡被其胞弟早良親王怨靈詛咒，天災人禍不斷。桓武天皇被迫遷都平安京，由此開啟四百年平安時代序幕。彼時權貴內部鬥爭激烈，人民生活疾苦，世間因此怨靈叢生，人、鬼與怪物屏息同棲。隸屬於宮廷陰陽寮的陰陽師們，作為平衡天、地、人、鬼間矛盾的存在，自此活躍在歷史舞台上，其中最為耀眼的便是身世成謎的安倍晴明（野村萬齋飾） 。右近衛中將源博雅（伊藤英明 飾）受託拜訪安倍晴明，被所目睹的奇異景象及晴明的個人魅力深深折服；晴明亦被博雅正直的品德吸引。故事便從兩人宿命相識，結下珍貴情誼開始...<br />\n<br />\n2.平安時代，百鬼夜行，封鬼儀式正在右大臣藤原安麻呂府邸進行。安麻呂之女日美子（深田恭子 飾）戎裝登場，一箭命中靶心，引來全場驚嘆。這位被喻為&ldquo;連鬼都不敢接近&rdquo;的公主，卻令源博雅（伊藤英明 飾）暗自傾心。天現異象，京都騷動，魍魎橫行。平安京已有四人遇害，民間出現驅鬼術士幻角（中井貴一 飾），日美子亦在異像後開始夢遊。博雅為此替右大臣來請安倍晴明（野村萬齋 飾）商談。與此同時，宮廷供奉的出云三神器之一草薙劍也出現了異動。晴明受天皇所託，與博雅開始調查種種異況背後出雲與大和的隱秘淵源<br />\n<br />\n10 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32822eeaaa8a0f0f1d29c2ac74ba849eb9e5ecd5","tid":304449,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602c3390590930a722b784b8df4b831da629e05f","tid":304449,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e7ef6f6014410c5851d7ed7a4735e3a91a277f","tid":304449,"uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969ac35744c445359d708f3b3d7287dc25454ef3","tid":304449,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:40:23.000Z","msg":"睇過 安倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3044b5c7ef5fcc6587ee25584e0c045069213e","tid":304449,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7083afc5896f35ac94931206c4de1a072c48147d","tid":304449,"uid":29160,"like"